name: RAFFLE.EXE
description: it took a lot of blood sweat and tears but i’ve finally found and recovered the last of my Windoze Premier Edition 1.0 disks, which is designed to help artists ensure their work is going to a good home when hosting a raffle. it’s a bit finicky on modern hardware though, and the anti-piracy functionality seems to be very buggy if your base system hasn’t been fully verified with your serial number...
